data.description: The Arden plan has a great open design. Kitchen features beautiful cabinets with extra lights over the gourmet granite counter height Island overlooking the spacious Living Room and Dining Room which is great for entertaining. Low maintenance Luxury Vinyl Wood Plank floors throughout the living area. Owner's suite offers a large walk-in closet and 5ft walk-in shower, double vanity and sinks. All of this is on a large homesite but minutes from beach enjoyment, coastal living and shopping in Emerald Isle and Swansboro. REQUEST INFO Home Is Connected® Smart Home Package is standard with every new home. Control the thermostat, front door light and lock, and video doorbell from your smartphone or with voice commands to Alexa! The photos you see here are for illustration purposes only, interior and exterior features, options, colors and selections will differ.
